# Auto-generated daily bake-off snapshot reports (aggregate_bakeoff.py emits
# evals/swebench/bake-off-YYYY-MM-DD.md). They're regenerable from the run dirs
# under evals/swebench/runs/; keeping them out of source control prevents a
# monthly accumulation of historical dated files.
evals/swebench/bake-off-2026-*.md
